    (versionName 0.6.7, versionCode 60700) so F-Droid autoupdate can track new
    releases from the git tags. No functional change.

 -- Adrian Scripca <benishor@gmail.com>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 21:00:00 +0300

xlog2 (0.6.6) noble; urgency=medium

  * Android/F-Droid: point libsodium's archive tools (AR/NM/RANLIB/STRIP) at the
    NDK's llvm-* binutils. NDK r26 ships only the llvm-prefixed tools, so
    configure otherwise fell back to the host nm and failed libtool's object-parse
    test on the F-Droid buildserver. Verified in a Debian trixie container.

 -- Adrian Scripca <benishor@gmail.com>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 20:00:00 +0300

xlog2 (0.6.5) noble; urgency=medium

  * Android/F-Droid: make the native-dep build portable — disable automake
    dependency tracking so libsodium's ./configure succeeds on the F-Droid
    buildserver (Debian trixie). No change to the produced app.
  * This tag carries the Fastlane store-listing metadata so F-Droid sources the
    app summary/description/changelog from the built commit.

 -- Adrian Scripca <benishor@gmail.com>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 19:00:00 +0300

